Board Battles — public site: content & data usage
==================================================

This repository contains a single baked artifact (`index.html`). Two different
things inside it carry two different licenses:

1. CODE (the site's HTML/CSS/JavaScript and the code that generated it) is
   released under the MIT License, which lives with the source in the separate
   Board Battles code repository. You may reuse the code under MIT.

2. DRAFT-RANKING DATA shown on the site is NOT open-licensed. Each ranking is the
   intellectual property of the scout or outlet that produced it and is used here
   for measurement and commentary, with attribution and links back to the
   source (see CREDITS.md). Paid/subscription sources are never reproduced as
   ordered boards or exact ranks — only derived measurements and coarse ranges.

Nothing here grants any right to redistribute the third-party ranking data.
Reuse of the code is free (MIT); reuse of the data is not.

Copyright (c) 2026 Brendan Martin. Independent project; not affiliated with the
NHL or any outlet graded. A human IP / media-law review is recommended before
wider public promotion.
